questions.question: A person is both above and inside an object o1. Later, the person is holding another object o2.
questions.dsl: (above(o0, o1), in(o0, o1), object(o0, 'person')); holding(o0, o2)

questions.question: An object o0 is above another object o1 and beneath a third object o2. Later, o0, which is a person, is sitting on o2.
A person is holding an object o1 and is also drinking from o1 while being inside of it.
questions.dsl: holding(o0, o1); (drinking_from(o0, o1), in(o0, o1), object(o0, 'person'))

questions.question: An object o0 is behind another object o1 and is touching a second object o2. Later, the same object o0, which is a person, is beneath o1.
A person is holding an object o1 and is also inside o1. Later, the person is in front of another object o2.
questions.dsl: (holding(o0, o1), in(o0, o1), object(o0, 'person')); in_front_of(o0, o2)

questions.question: Initially, a person is behind an object o1 and is drinking from it. Later, the person is inside the same object o1.
A person is standing on an object o1. Then, the same person is holding another object o2 while being in front of it.
A person o0 is holding an object o1 while being inside another object o2. Later, the person is drinking from o2.
An object o0 is in front of another object o1. Later, the same object o0, which is a person, is beneath o1 and is standing on a third object o2.
questions.dsl: in_front_of(o0, o1); (beneath(o0, o1), object(o0, 'person'), standing_on(o0, o2))

questions.question: A person is beneath another object o1 and is eating o1. Later, the person is in front of o1.
questions.dsl: (beneath(o0, o1), eating(o0, o1), object(o0, 'person')); in_front_of(o0, o1)
